{"tid":2385998,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"義務急救員出營返家遭截查 被控管有攻擊性武器今獲判無罪","createTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:13:24.000Z","uid":56115,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b5db0141069ef4ad19d6c446b63002eebf7b27","tid":2385998,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"學生義務急救員於反修例抗爭期間宿營返家，途中遇上防暴警截査，被搜出藏有附帶刀鋒的多用途手繩、卡片刀及防具，被拘控以管有攻擊性武器罪。案件早前審結，裁判官梁雅忻今裁決謂：「中肯地說，物品似乎用嚟整爛或者打開一啲嘢多啲，對用嚟傷人則有保留。」最終裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n梁官裁決時指，涉案警員證供清晰、直接、沒有誇大，接納警員是誠實可靠證人。<span class=\"red\">惟涉案卡片刀及附有刀鋒手繩，均未能被定義為攻擊性武器物品，兩件物品均附有多功能用途。</span><br />\n<br />\n惟梁官最後補充指，被告身懷多種被懷疑涉案物品，行為絕對是自招嫌疑，故<span class=\"red\">下令充公涉案物品。</span>"},{"pid":"3cda47d63885bffed66ff5b3a7b56be1237cf34d","tid":2385998,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/U6USATCNWNCV7CWWLZB56SUKWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FU6USATCNWNCV7CWWLZB56SUKWY%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wwCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=d2e0d8ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210129%2FU6USATCNWNCV7CWWLZB56SUKWY%2F&h=8a78c877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210129/U6USATCNWNCV7CWWLZB56SUKWY/</a>"},{"pid":"075b9bb247eccff8aa5ec12f4003447c502985f6","tid":2385998,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2d13d78da33dc90b152613090b9f3ba496c64b","tid":2385998,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"律政司等陣上訴"},{"pid":"7641fa284f79ad4647b703c442d684bf2393794e","tid":2385998,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no